org.gephi.datalab.plugin.manipulators.columns

Class CreateFoundGroupsListColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gephi.datalab.plugin.manipulators.columns.GeneralCreateColumnFromRegex
      • org.gephi.datalab.plugin.manipulators.columns.CreateFoundGroupsListColumn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeColumnsManipulator

    public class CreateFoundGroupsListColumn
extends GeneralCreateColumnFromRegex
    AttributeColumnsManipulator that creates a new string list column from the given column and regular expression with values that are the list of matching groups of the given regular expression. Allows the user to select the title of the new column in the UI
    Author:
    Eduardo Ramos
